OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,FWestminster is facing a "summer of
OL,7,Fdiscontent" with the future of both
OL,8,Fthe Prime Minister and his Government
OL,9,F"in limbo", the SNP has claimed.
OL,11,FDave Doogan, the party's Westminster
OL,12,Fleader, hit out at the "chaos" in the
OL,13,FUK Government in the wake of the
OL,14,Flatest resignations from Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer's top team, claiming Labour is
OL,16,Fnow "entering a full blown civil war".
OL,26,@nD@YOUoD@KO]qD@AOUqD@JO]tD@XOUtD@^O]xD@
OL,26,AEOUxD@eO]
