PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781308974
OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,FHe said: "Labour's chaos means that
OL,7,FWestminster is set for another summer
OL,8,Fof discontent ` the public is left
OL,9,Fwith a Prime Minister and a UK
OL,10,FGovernment literally living in limbo."
OL,12,FHis comments came as the PM's fragile
OL,13,Fauthority suffered a further blow
OL,14,Fearlier this week with the resignation
OL,15,Fof defence secretary John Healey, who
OL,16,Fclaimed UK spending on defence "falls
OL,17,Fwell short of what is required" to
OL,18,Fkeep the country safe.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@fO]xD@`OUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
