PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781308974
OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,FThat was quickly followed by Al Carns
OL,7,Fquitting as armed forces minister,
OL,8,Falong with two ministerial aides.
OL,10,FThey are the latest resignations to
OL,11,Fhit the Government over the course of
OL,12,Frecent weeks, following the departure
OL,13,Fof health secretary Wes Streeting and
OL,14,Fa number of junior figures who left
OL,15,Ftheir posts in the wake of Labour's
OL,16,Fbruising election defeats across
OL,17,FScotland, England and Wales in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
