FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781308974
OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,FMeanwhile the Makerfield by-election
OL,7,Fon Thursday could see Andy Burnham `
OL,8,Fwho has made no secret of his Labour
OL,9,Fleadership ambitions ` return to the
OL,10,FCommons, with Mr Streeting also
OL,11,Fexpected to run in any contest to
OL,12,Fsucceed Sir Keir.
OL,14,FMr Doogan said: "The raft of
OL,15,Fresignations in the last few days is
OL,16,Fconfirmation that the Labour Party is
OL,17,Fentering into a full-blown civil war,
OL,18,Fbut as usual it is the public who will
OL,19,Fbe left to count the cost of their
OL,20,Fchaos.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
