PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781308974
OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,F"Every single day that the Labour
OL,7,FParty are focused on fighting amongst
OL,8,Fthemselves is one more day they will
OL,9,Fignore the priorities of the people
OL,10,Fthey are actually there to serve.
OL,12,F"People gave Labour their trust to be
OL,13,Fa responsible Government, instead they
OL,14,Fhave been reckless from the very day
OL,15,Fthey took office.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
