PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781308974
OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,F"For years, Labour politicians
OL,7,Farrogantly lectured others about
OL,8,Fgetting on with the day job ` now they
OL,9,Fcan't even get through a full week
OL,10,Fwithout another resignation or another
OL,11,Fscandal."
OL,13,FHe said "in the real world ` the cost-
OL,14,Fof-living emergency deepens for
OL,15,Ffamilies, with energy bills set to
OL,16,Fsoar by over #200 at the start of
OL,17,FJuly".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@IOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
