PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781308974
OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,FWhile Mr Doogan accepted "all
OL,7,Fpolitical parties face their
OL,8,Fchallenges", he said it is
OL,9,F"unforgivable that in Westminster
OL,10,Fthose challenges constantly consume
OL,11,Fthe job of Government".
OL,13,FThe SNP MP said: "Chaos is now the
OL,14,Fpermanent pattern of Westminster and a
OL,15,Fgeneration of our people have been
OL,16,Fleft to pay the price of that damage
OL,17,Fand decline."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@KO]qD@AOUsD@VO]uD@ROUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
