CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781308974
OL,3,CLabour facing 'summer of discontent'
OL,4,Cwith Starmer 'in limbo', claims SNP
OL,6,FHe sought to contrast the situation
OL,7,Fsouth of the border with the "reliable
OL,8,Fleadership of John Swinney" as SNP
OL,9,Fleader and Scottish First Minister.
OL,11,FMr Doogan vowed: "The SNP won't let
OL,12,Fthe distraction of Westminster's chaos
OL,13,Fstop us from focusing on the
OL,14,Fpriorities of the Scottish people.
OL,16,F"The SNP will get on with the job of
OL,17,FGovernment and keep delivering on our
OL,18,Fpromises with new support for first-
OL,19,Ftime buyers, a massive childcare
OL,20,Fexpansion, and more progress in
OL,21,Fbringing down NHS waiting lists.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@[O]sD@ROUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
